-- GM estimates U.S. share over 26 percent in August
-- 
-- Tue Sep 4, 2007 2:42pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/09/04/us-gm-sales-share-idUSN0439909820070904

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - General Motors Corp ( GM.N ) said on Tuesday that it estimates its U.S. market share for August was above 26 percent, the highest level of the year. 

 The automaker, which posted over 5 percent increase in August sales, said sales to commercial fleets rose 21 percent last month. GM's showroom sales were flat during the month, GM's chief sales analyst Paul Ballew told reporters on a conference call. (Reporting by  Poornima Gupta )